OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMan given 'wife's ashes'   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbefore her cremation       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A grandfather claims he was given what 
OL,6, he was told were his wife's ashes only 
OL,7, to discover that she had not been      
OL,8, cremated until several weeks later.    
OL,10,FPeter Welburn said he paid #1,900 to   
OL,11,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors,  
OL,12,Fwhich is at the centre of a police     
OL,13,Finvestigation, for his wife Shirley's  
OL,14,Ffuneral.                               
OL,16,FHe claims he received the ashes on 23  
OL,17,FDecember but said he was told this week
OL,18,Fthat his wife was not cremated until 16
OL,19,FJanuary.                               
OL,21,FThe BBC has contacted Legacy.          
